Question.Subject: my browser keeps going to webresults6.org?
Question.Content: every time i do a Google search and click on one of the links my browser will go to webresults6.org instead of the page its supposed to...it works fine if i type the website in the address bar and only does it if i try to search something in a search engine then try to click on one of the results. oh yea it is also a fresh install of windows XP professional and this happens on all my browsers...firefox, IE, Opera, and google chrome
